    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the Prime Minister, through the proper diplomatic channels, make it clear to the Soviet Government <span id="1503" class="column-number" data-column-number="1503"></span> that the vast majority of people in this country wish them well and hope that they will sincerely take part in an advance towards world peace?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
